<h1>My Account</h1>
<h3>Balance</h3>
<p>
You can view the current balance in your account by using this option.
Enter your 4-digit PIN to authenticate your request.
Click on 'Back' to go back to the previous page.</p>
<h3>History</h3>
<p>
You can view the history of your past transactions by using this option.
Enter your 4-digit PIN to authenticate your request.
Click on 'Back' to go back to the previous page.</p>
<h3>Change PIN</h3>
<p>
To change your PIN, enter your current PIN and set a new PIN. Re-enter the new PIN to confirm. 
Click on 'Back' to go back to the previous page.</p>
<p>
Contact <%CUSTOMER_CARE%> if you need help.
</p>
